[CONTENT WARNING] This post and the following caption reference suicide and may be triggering. 

For the next two years, we’re partnering with The Trevor Project in support of their mission to end LGBTQIA+ youth suicide. 

We’ll be sharing The Trevor Project’s research, tips and resources, so that we can all be more educated and equipped to support LGBTQIA+ youth. 

Learn more about The Trevor Project. Link in bio. 

If you are thinking about suicide and looking for immediate support, call the TrevorLifeline at 1-866-488-7386. 

#proudinmycalvins
